videos.description: R.J. Cole fires a pass from the logo into the paint for Adama Sanogo who manages to lay it in while being fouled.

videos.description: After standing on the court talking on his phone, UConn alum and Hornets guard James Bouknight was ejected during the Huskies' matchup vs. Xavier.
